      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST TAKE IT (4) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when third (19.97) at this track over 340m. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Top chance in this line up. TILLY CARGO (6) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at this track over 340m behind Irinka Nina (20.49) in a Maiden. Has good speed so she should be prominent despite the draw. Deserves plenty of respect. BLOCKER'S MATE (2) produced a moderate run last time when fourth at this track over 340m behind Irinka Nina (20.23). Can measure up this time. HOOLIGAN TOMMY (1) is a newcomer from the Kevin Sills kennel. Drawn well and should get his chance. Expected to produce a bold debut.",
